<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Damai Sejahtera di Tengah Ketidakpastian - Sekolah Teologi</title>
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
      
      body { 
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; 
        margin: 0; 
        padding: 0; 
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      
      .container { 
        max-width: 800px; 
        margin: 0 auto; 
        padding: 3rem 2rem; 
        text-align: center; 
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      }
      
      .error-code { 
        font-size: 6rem; 
        font-weight: 300; 
        color: #0ea5e9; 
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
      }
      
      .title { 
        font-size: 2.5rem; 
        font-weight: 600; 
        color: #1e293b; 
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }
      
      .scripture {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #475569;
        font-style: italic;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        background: #f8fafc;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
        max-width: 500px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }
      
      .description { 
        font-size: 1.2rem; 
        color: #64748b; 
        margin-bottom: 3rem; 
        max-width: 42rem; 
        margin-left: auto; 
        margin-right: auto;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-weight: 400;
      }
      
      .btn-container {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }
      
      .btn { 
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        padding: 1rem 2rem; 
        border-radius: 12px; 
        font-weight: 500; 
        text-decoration: none; 
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      
      .btn-primary { 
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #0284c7 100%); 
        color: white; 
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);
      }
      
      .btn-primary:hover { 
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.4);
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0284c7 0%, #0369a1 100%);
      }
      
      .btn-secondary { 
        border: 2px solid #0ea5e9; 
        color: #0ea5e9; 
        background: transparent;
      }
      
      .btn-secondary:hover { 
        background: #f0f9ff; 
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.2);
      }
      
      .explore-section {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      }
      
      .explore-title {
        font-size: 1.25rem; 
        font-weight: 600; 
        color: #1e293b; 
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      
      .explore-links {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      
      .explore-link {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        background: #f8fafc;
        color: #475569;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      
      .explore-link:hover {
        background: #e0f2fe;
        color: #0ea5e9;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
      
      .peace-icon {
        font-size: 4rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        opacity: 0.7;
      }
      
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .container {
          margin: 1rem;
          padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .error-code {
          font-size: 4rem;
        }
        
        .title {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }
        
        .btn-container {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
        }
        
        .btn {
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 250px;
          justify-content: center;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="peace-icon">üïäÔ∏è</div>
      <div class="error-code">404</div>
      <h1 class="title">Damai Sejahtera di Tengah Ketidakpastian</h1>
      
      <div class="scripture">
        "Damai sejahtera Kutinggalkan bagimu. Damai sejahtera-Ku Kuberikan kepadamu, 
        dan apa yang Kuberikan tidak seperti yang diberikan oleh dunia kepadamu. 
        Janganlah gelisah dan gentar hatimu." - Yohanes 14:27
      </div>
      
      <p class="description">
        Meskipun halaman yang Anda cari tidak ditemukan, ingatlah bahwa dalam Kristus 
        kita selalu menemukan jalan. Biarlah damai sejahtera-Nya yang melampaui segala akal 
        memelihara hati dan pikiran Anda.
      </p>
      
      <div class="btn-container">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
          üè† Kembali ke Beranda
        </a>
        <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-secondary">
          ‚Ü©Ô∏è Kembali ke Halaman Sebelumnya
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="explore-section">
        <h3 class="explore-title">Temukan Damai Sejahtera dalam:</h3>
        <div class="explore-links">
          <a href="/renungan" class="explore-link">Renungan Harian</a>
          <a href="/edukasi" class="explore-link">Edukasi Teologi</a>
          <a href="/doa" class="explore-link">Panduan Doa</a>
          <a href="/kontak" class="explore-link">Konseling & Dukungan</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div style="margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #94a3b8;">
        <p>"Marilah kepada-Ku, semua yang letih lesu dan berbeban berat, Aku akan memberi kelegaan kepadamu." - Matius 11:28</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script>
      // Tambahkan efek ketikan untuk ayat Alkitab
      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
        const scripture = document.querySelector('.scripture');
        const originalText = scripture.textContent;
        scripture.textContent = '';
        
        let i = 0;
        function typeWriter() {
          if (i < originalText.length) {
            scripture.textContent += originalText.charAt(i);
            i++;
            setTimeout(typeWriter, 30);
          }
        }
        
        // Mulai efek ketikan setelah delay kecil
        setTimeout(typeWriter, 1000);
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>